================================================================================
Attribution for upstream and reference projects
================================================================================

trafilaturacore is a hybrid Rust + TypeScript content-extraction library derived from
Trafilatura. Its boilerplate-removal + page-type-classification core is a Rust
crate (packages/trafilaturacore/native/) — a simplified fork of rs-trafilatura's live
extraction path — reached from Node via napi-rs; the public API, HTML-cleaning
levels, metadata sidecar, and CLI stay TypeScript. The projects below fall into
two kinds: those trafilaturacore is DERIVED FROM (their code is ported or copied and
ships in this package — attribution required by their licenses), and those
CONSULTED as design/idiom references (no code shipped — credited as a courtesy).
Each entry states which. The text of the Apache License, Version 2.0 referenced
below is reproduced in this repository's LICENSE file.

