Trafilatura (the canonical original) — Apache-2.0
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------
Author:  Adrien Barbaresi
Source:  https://github.com/adbar/trafilatura
Docs:    https://trafilatura.readthedocs.io/

DERIVED FROM (attribution required). The canonical original. trafilaturacore's metadata
subsystem (packages/trafilaturacore/src/metadata/*) is a direct TypeScript port of its
